-- Euro Extends Drop as Report Shows Region’s Recession Deepened
-- B y   L u c y   M e a k i n
-- 2013-02-14T10:04:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-14/euro-extends-drop-as-report-shows-region-s-recession-deepened.html
The euro extended its decline
against the dollar and yen after a report showed the region’s
recession deepened.  The currency slid 0.8 percent to $1.3340 as of 10:03 a.m.
London time. It weakened 0.7 percent to 124.80 yen.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucy Meakin in London at 
